                                                                 <a href=https://www.harvardartmuseums.org/collections/person/29186>Adriaen van de Velde</a>, Dutch                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          (Amsterdam, Netherlands 1636 - 1672 Amsterdam, Netherlands)
                                            <br>
                                    </dd>
            
                            <dt>Title</dt>
                <dd>Study of a Seated Boy</dd>
            
                                                                                                            
